description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from Vocaloid!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・World's End Dancehall
・We Are Different !!! (or Same)
・Comet Honeymoon
・I wanna be it !
・Suicide Parade
・Venom *Tokino Sora Bonus Cover Song Included!
・Otome Kaibou
・Zettai Ni Chocomint Wo Taberu Aoichan
・Villain
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・flower  (V4)
・Una Otomachi

■Avatar
・Una Otomachi(Spicy)
・Una Otomachi(Sugar)
・Una Otomachi(2D)
・flower(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 4
